  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Service Crew",
  "description": "<p><strong>Introduction:</strong></p><p>Casa Vostra is excited to share that due to the success of its first physical outlet in Raffles City Shopping Centre, we are planning to open our second outlet in the West where customers are able to access restaurant-quality Italian pizzas and pastas. </p><p><br /></p><p>We invite you to be a part of shaping these incredible dining experiences with us! If you’re someone who takes joy in connecting with others and creating warm, welcoming atmospheres, we’d love for you to join our service family.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Warmly welcome and assist guest with their orders</li><li>Assist with the supervisor with daily opening and closing of the outlet</li><li>Build and maintain excellent relationship with guest</li><li>Make menu recommendations to guest with extensive menu knowledge</li><li>Ensure smooth floor service by serving guest in a timely manner</li></ul><p><strong>Qualifications:</strong></p><ul><li>No experience needed just a teachable heart</li><li>Passion for Italian cuisine and hospitality</li><li>Ability to work in a fast pace environment</li></ul><p><strong>Perks:</strong></p><ul><li>Birthday Leave to spend with loved ones on your special day</li><li>Competitive Staff Discounts across outlets</li><li>Health and Medical Insurance coverage</li><li>Opportunity to learn from knowledgeable mentors in the industry</li></ul><p>If you’re a passionate individual with a strong work ethic, we invite you to apply!</p>",
